{"tid":23203,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我最愛嗰嗰，你同我入嚟","createTime":"2016-12-04T19:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T14:41:10.000Z","uid":22830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a12c8bf9e58b2af88f8328416907aee7685efd2","tid":23203,"uid":22830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:55:02.000Z","msg":"好掛住一開始嘅你同我<br />\n唔知你仲記唔記得當初個種好強烈嘅感覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到對方爆擦 <br />\n好心靈相通咁買潤唇膏比對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我飲醉咗你迫我食湯圓 仲要加薑<br />\n你對我嘅好 我全部都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以為同你走到最後嗰嗰 會係我<br />\n話想保護我 照顧我 應承我唔會掉低我<br />\n但原來一直對我嘅愛 <br />\n係出於憐憫 出於一種責任感<br />\n最後你選擇離開我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想放低你 但對唔住我做唔到<br />\n我好想你返嚟我身邊<br />\n聽你講 跟感覺走 我會一直等你 守護你<br />\n直到你搵到你真正愛嘅人為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好再自責喇傻瓜 無怪過你<br />\n只係好想你幸福同開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你睇到啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後一句，我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b3e8b17df18afb4e00b25a400f1bb060122866","tid":23203,"uid":21782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打加油"},{"pid":"a3326d0e7bbafc10fe30f1947b7c8e7505b2892a","tid":23203,"uid":50298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T20:09:07.000Z","msg":"我都愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7999e3124e70b0cb055cbc3d7e35ffc3ba8ddcca","tid":23203,"uid":22830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T20:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打加油</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw我係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00a7b9292a19993bcfb1e26b9a00094cb5e645d","tid":23203,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T20:39:38.000Z","msg":"鬧唔鬧得？"},{"pid":"01e9887328f0984739018df37da9f8c436bcbe34","tid":23203,"uid":22830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T20:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬧唔鬧得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n任屌唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553105010e777096d55865e8e9f6dfdc47c911c4","tid":23203,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T21:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鬧唔鬧得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n任屌唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁順攤唔想鬧"},{"pid":"4be350c0d1a87963932c9f190eeea2164cde23f1","tid":23203,"uid":22830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T21:22:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鬧唔鬧得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n任屌唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁順攤唔想鬧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 指點下"},{"pid":"d0e3693c8933c8e39cf055e895813722837ab147","tid":23203,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T21:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鬧唔鬧得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n任屌唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁順攤唔想鬧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 指點下</blockquote><br />\n冇啦啦指點咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9af12cbf8dbe2bf5b2300afa2005b7c7986ffc1","tid":23203,"uid":22830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB